        {
            "type": "prose",
            "fields": {
                "heading": "Everything a care provider needs on staffing",
                "body": "Running a care service in London means keeping shifts covered, staying CQC-ready and controlling agency spend at the same time. This resources hub brings together our practical guides for registered managers and care providers: how CQC compliance and staffing fit together, how temporary staffing solves rota gaps without cutting corners, and what to look for when hiring healthcare assistants. Each guide is written from real care-sector experience, not generic advice. Vigil Care Staffing supplies directly vetted, DBS-checked care workers across Greater London and responds to every query within 15 minutes, so when you need cover as well as guidance, one call reaches both. Use the guides below to plan your workforce, then talk to our team about the specific cover you need."
            },
